{"tid":1500502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大肚婆因党鐵停駛，導致未能去醫院生b，mtr發起不合作運動 mtr係亂港分子","createTime":"2019-08-24T04:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T05:08:10.000Z","uid":201732,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb4519686473b79544bbb333a54f9b5b41f4fcb","tid":1500502,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大肚婆因党鐵停駛，導致未能去醫院生b，mtr發起不合作運動 mtr係亂港分子</span>"},{"pid":"6cd530fbdb9197f990c70e394caff33ba91155ef","tid":1500502,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命嗰陣 <br />\n因為佔用馬路佔得太耐 <br />\n開始搞到中立、港豬、淺黃淺藍都鬧示威者<br />\n<br />\n今次反送中運動我哋學精左<br />\n唔再搞長期佔領<br />\n塞鐵活動搞手都順應民意唔再搞<br />\n大部份中立、港豬、淺黃淺藍企係我哋嗰邊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府冇晒符嘅時候<br />\n竟然自己封地鐵<br />\n以後一有遊行即刻封地鐵<br />\n然後就賴落示威者度</span><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋一定要大力文宣<br />\n同封地鐵劃清界線<br />\n講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封地鐵嘅係政府</span>而唔係示威者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以前遊行一路地鐵暢順無阻</span><br />\n示威者都順應民意唔搞封地鐵<br />\n影響民生、傢禍示威者嘅係政府<br />\n我哋要民生受影響嘅人都加入反政府嘅行列<br />\n民意繼續更加倒向我哋呢邊"},{"pid":"7807ba8219f519f35a7c6eb38cb7dca45631a89f","tid":1500502,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQvChfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQvChfO.png&h=a3736a13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01f8a856a6e82b61f9f7de2089c071ee022a3c0f","tid":1500502,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wbIlxjNbegQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwbIlxjNbegQ&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=64544759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wbIlxjNbegQ</a>"}]}